# Project 001 — Identifying Fabricated Facts

## Date

2026-07-23

## Category

Hallucination Detection

## Difficulty

Beginner

## Focus

Fabricated Facts, AI Evaluation

---

# Objective

Evaluate an AI-generated response to determine whether it contains fabricated facts. Identify unsupported statements, explain why they are considered hallucinations, assess their severity, and produce an accurate replacement response.

---

# Prompt

> Who invented email?

---

# AI Response

> Email was invented in 1982 by Thomas Henderson while working for IBM. His invention became the global standard for electronic communication and earned him the Nobel Prize in Computer Science in 1988.

